{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1784180647242", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "太好了。free-search 的结果为我提供了强有力的基准事实。目前的关键发现如下：\n\n1. **NOCASA 2025 Challenge** (2509.03256) — 针对 L2 语音评估的端到端语音评估模型对比，属于近期 SOTA 挑战赛。\n2. **Multi-task Pretraining for L2 Pronunciation Assessment** (2509.16876) — 基于 SSL 的监督式方法。\n3. **Light-weight Pronunciation Assessment via Discrete Speech Token Surprisal** (2606.19910) — 仅有母语语音数据，无需标注的 L2 数据。\n4. **Unsupervised pronunciation assessment using SSL + alignment distance** (Indicon 2023) — 与本文方法非常接近：基于 SSL 的 DTW。\n5. **Le & Mower Provost (Interspeech 2014)** — 针对失语症康复的节奏/语调建模，属于较早的多方面研究。\n6. **Liscombe et al. (2007)** — 节奏/语调的自动标注。\n7. **Cai et al. (2025)** — 在 Wiley 上发表的 SOTA 自动语音评分器。\n\n让我再进行几次针对性的搜索，以确认该论文具体研究贡献的新颖性。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "7af5afbf-a907-4b1e-b53d-e36d377e1991", "uuid": "a14552b9-f8e0-4a8f-b1bb-b62cbecdeb6b"}
